	                	<h3 style="text-align: center;color:#0000ff;">
	NEW PRODUCT: BIOGAS-DIESEL COMPACT ENGINE</h3>
<div style="text-align: justify;">
	<div>
		GATEC developped new model of biogas-diesel compact engine that is very suitable for using biogas fuel in various circumstances.</div>
	<div>
		It&rsquo;s a compact engine, quite the same diesel engine, but with a twin speed governors: one for biogas control and another for diesel control.</div>
	<div>
		The engine operates mainly with biogas and diesel pilot injection for ignition (dual fuel biogas-diesel). It can switch on diesel if necessary without any special technical intervention.</div>
