											<h1 class="title">
				Biogas Mixer for SI Engine				</h1>
									<div class="clear"></div>
				</div>
		<div class="module-content">
			
			
			<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>MIXER DESIGN FOR A HIGH PERFORMANCE BIOGAS<br />
	SI ENGINE CONVERTED FROM AN <span class="m29xg" id="m29xg_2">DIESEL ENGINE</span></strong></span></span><br />
	&nbsp;<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);"><strong>Bui Van Ga, Tran Van Nam</strong><br />
	<em>The University of Danang</em><br />
	<em>41 Le Duan, Danang, Vietnam</em><br />
	<em>Email: 
